title: Stargazer 2: Displacement Vector | Creative Commons PDF eBook Sc
description:
Two years after the BlackHole Recovery Incident, Faith and Nick are again thrust into the spotlight in a crisis of human-alien relations.

There is a mysterious killer on the loose - with a grand end-game in mind. The Vice President has been taken captive. A shadowy villain lurks behind it all.

This globetrotting tale takes the reader to the farthest recesses of the planet, as well as the farthest reaches of our solar system...
